// publisher.md → PublisherName, invoiceissuer.md → InvoiceIssuerName):
//
//	1.0: https://github.com/FinOps-Open-Cost-and-Usage-Spec/FOCUS_Spec/tree/v1.0/specification/columns
//	1.1: https://github.com/FinOps-Open-Cost-and-Usage-Spec/FOCUS_Spec/tree/v1.1/specification/columns
