//
// (1.0/1.1/1.2 use the flat pre-1.3 specification/columns/ path — use tag v1.0,
// NOT 1.0-cr, whose consumedunit.md carries a Column-ID typo; some 1.0/1.1 files
// are CRLF, so trailing \r is trimmed. 1.3+ moved columns under
// specification/datasets/cost_and_usage/columns/.)
//
// Pinned counts (asserted in the tests): known 43 / 50 / 57 / 65 / 65;
// Mandatory-presence 21 / 21 / 21 / 23 / 21. FOCUS 1.0 ⊂ 1.1 ⊂ 1.2 with ZERO
