// Mandatory-presence sets are byte-identical. Between 1.3 and 1.4 zero columns
// were renamed (63 shared byte-identical); 1.4 removed ProviderName and
// PublisherName and added the nullable Conditional
// CommitmentProgramEligibilityDetails and InvoiceDetailId.

